*
 * Element for combining multiple routers {BaseRouter}s into one.
 *
 * @example
 * <router1 id="router1"></router1>
 * <router2 id="router2"></router2>
 *
 * <union-router routers="#router1,#router2"
 *     start="lat,lon"
 *     dest="lat,lon"
 *     time="now">
 * </union-router>

*
     * Sets a list of routers
